+-------+------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| OWNER | MVIEW_NAME | CONTAINER_NAME | QUERY                                                                                                                                                 |
+-------+------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| test  | zc_mv1     | zc_mv1         | select `ZT1`.`c1` AS `c1`,`ZT1`.`pk` AS `PK`,`ZT1`.`c2` AS `C2`,count(*) AS `cnt` from `test`.`zc_t1` `ZT1` group by `ZT1`.`c1`,`ZT1`.`c2`,`ZT1`.`pk` |
| test  | zc_mv2     | zc_mv2         | select `ZT2`.`c1` AS `c1`,`ZT2`.`pk` AS `PK`,`ZT2`.`c2` AS `C2`,count(*) AS `cnt` from `test`.`zc_t2` `ZT2` group by `ZT2`.`c1`,`ZT2`.`c2`,`ZT2`.`pk` |
| test  | zc_mv3     | zc_mv3         | select `ZT3`.`c1` AS `c1`,`ZT3`.`pk` AS `PK`,`ZT3`.`c2` AS `C2`,count(*) AS `cnt` from `test`.`zc_t3` `ZT3` group by `ZT3`.`c1`,`ZT3`.`c2`,`ZT3`.`pk` |
| test  | zc_mv4     | zc_mv4         | select `ZT4`.`c1` AS `c1`,`ZT4`.`pk` AS `PK`,`ZT4`.`c2` AS `C2`,count(*) AS `cnt` from `test`.`zc_t4` `ZT4` group by `ZT4`.`c1`,`ZT4`.`c2`,`ZT4`.`pk` |
+-------+------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
CREATE MATERIALIZED VIEW LOG ON oceanbase.DBA_MVIEWS parallel 2 WITH ROWID,SEQUENCE(OWNER,MVIEW_NAME,CONTAINER_NAME,REFRESH_MODE) INCLUDING NEW VALUES;
